file.content:
openapi: "3.0.0"
info:
  version: 1.0.0
  title: Object example validations
paths:
  /check-dict:
    get:
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Checking example dict
          content:
            'application/json':
              schema:
                type: object
                properties:
                  integer:
                    type: integer
                  real:
                    type: number
                example:
                  integer: 42
                  real: 0.5
  /check-str:
    get:
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Checking example string
          content:
            'text/plain':
                example: 'Hello'

Error: notImplemented: path "/check-str": get: responses: 200: contents: unsupported content types: [text/plain]
